title: Week 15 NFL Recap, Analysis; Cowboys cruise, Evidence against the Patriots? (Football 12/16)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap all the Week 15 action from around the NFL. The guys discuss all 14 games on the Sunday slate including Bills-Steelers (3:20), Cowboys-Rams (14:40), Eagles-Redskins (29:00), Bengals-Patriots (41:20), Panthers-Seahawks/Falcons-49ers (54:30), Bears-Packers/Vikings-Chargers (1:07:00), Texans-Titans (1:21:15), Broncos-Chiefs (1:30:00), Jaguars-Raiders (1:33:45), Browns-Cardinals (1:40:50), Dolphins-Giants (1:45:30), and Bucs-Lions (1:48:15).
